OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1777655154
OL,3,CEx-officer admits misconduct over
OL,4,Crelationship with victim
OL,6,FA former police officer has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to misconduct after a
OL,8,Frelationship with a crime victim
OL,9,Flasting more than six years.
OL,11,FChristopher Cave, of Formby in
OL,12,FLiverpool, started a sexual
OL,13,Frelationship with the victim while
OL,14,Fworking as an officer in
OL,15,FNottinghamshire in 2004. The
OL,16,Frelationship continued until early
OL,17,F2011.
OL,19,FThe allegations made against Cave, now
OL,20,Faged 61, were brought to the attention
OL,21,Fof South Yorkshire Police in 2022.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
