FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1777655154
OL,3,CEx-officer admits misconduct over
OL,4,Crelationship with victim
OL,6,FHe was arrested and suspended from
OL,7,Fduties in June that year.
OL,9,FCave, who had been an officer in South
OL,10,FYorkshire between 2010 and 2017, had
OL,11,Freturned to work as an evidence review
OL,12,Fofficer as part of a retirement scheme
OL,13,Favailable to people who have served
OL,14,Ffor more than 30 years.
OL,16,FHe officially resigned from the force
OL,17,Fin December 2023.
OL,19,FFollowing the conclusion of criminal
OL,20,Fproceedings an internal misconduct
OL,21,Fprocess will go ahead, the force said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
