PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1777655154
OL,3,CEx-officer admits misconduct over
OL,4,Crelationship with victim
OL,6,FCave admitted two counts of misconduct
OL,7,Fin a public office at Sheffield Crown
OL,8,FCourt and will be sentenced in June.
OL,10,FDet Con Nicola Milner said: "Being a
OL,11,Fpolice officer is a privileged role.
OL,13,F"It comes with a great deal of
OL,14,Fresponsibility and a requirement to
OL,15,Fuphold the highest levels of
OL,16,Fprofessionalism and public service.
OL,17,FThis is something Cave clearly abused
OL,18,Fand fell short of.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
