PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1777655154
OL,3,CEx-officer admits misconduct over
OL,4,Crelationship with victim
OL,6,F"His conduct over several years falls
OL,7,Ffar below what is expected from our
OL,8,Fworkforce and does not reflect our
OL,9,Fvalues of policing. We are committed
OL,10,Fto being open and transparent about
OL,11,Four officers' conduct and the victim
OL,12,Fin this case remains at the forefront
OL,13,Fof our minds. We now await sentencing
OL,14,Fin June."
